name: Laptops
description:
Engineering Good provides laptops to the needy through partner organisations i.e. you have to be a registered VWO to apply for these laptops.

You may request laptops directly with us via request4laptops@engineeringgood.org

This is our laptop refurbishing programme which we have run since 2020, where old laptops are collected and refurbished, and given to the needy. 

You will need to collect the laptop(s) at our office in B-Central, which is 5mins walk from Boon Keng MRT station.

For more information about the programme, see https://engineeringgood.org/digital-inclusion/cac/
